Title: Exact Heavy To Light Meson Form Factors In The Chiral Limit Of Planar
  1+1 QCD
Authors: Benjamin Grinstein
Comments: 8p (uuencoded, includes 4 eps figs, LaTeX & epsf), SMU-HEP/94-11 and
  UCSD/PTH 94-09
\\
  The form factors of the flavor changing vector current between a $\bar q
Q$-meson and the lightest $\bar q q$ (pseudoscalar-)meson are computed exactly
and explicitly in the 't~Hooft model (planar QCD in $1+1$ dimensions) in the
limit that the mass of $q$-quark vanishes.
